					<description><![CDATA[Cài đặt và cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN Bài viết này mình sẽ hướng dẫn cài đặt và cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN phiên bản miễn phí Để tải bản cài đặt các bạn có thể truy cập trang chủ Starwind tại https://www.starwindsoftware.com/ 1 &#8211; Cài đặt Starwind Virtual SAN Next để bắt đầu Chấp <a class="more-link" href="./../../../cai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san/index.html">Read More ...</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=.%2F%2Fcai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san%2F&amp;linkname=C%C3%A0i%20%C4%91%E1%BA%B7t%20v%C3%A0%20c%E1%BA%A5u%20h%C3%ACnh%20Starwind%20Virtual%20SAN" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=.%2F%2Fcai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san%2F&amp;linkname=C%C3%A0i%20%C4%91%E1%BA%B7t%20v%C3%A0%20c%E1%BA%A5u%20h%C3%ACnh%20Starwind%20Virtual%20SAN" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=.%2F%2Fcai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san%2F&amp;linkname=C%C3%A0i%20%C4%91%E1%BA%B7t%20v%C3%A0%20c%E1%BA%A5u%20h%C3%ACnh%20Starwind%20Virtual%20SAN" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=.%2F%2Fcai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san%2F&#038;title=C%C3%A0i%20%C4%91%E1%BA%B7t%20v%C3%A0%20c%E1%BA%A5u%20h%C3%ACnh%20Starwind%20Virtual%20SAN" data-a2a-url="./../../../cai-dat-va-cau-hinh-starwind-virtual-san/index.html" data-a2a-title="Cài đặt và cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN"></a></p><p><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>Cài đặt và cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN</strong></span></p>
<p>Bài viết này mình sẽ hướng dẫn cài đặt và cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN phiên bản miễn phí</p>
<p>Để tải bản cài đặt các bạn có thể truy cập trang chủ Starwind tại <a href="https://www.starwindsoftware.com/" target="_blank">https://www.starwindsoftware.com/</a></p>
<p><strong>1 &#8211; Cài đặt Starwind Virtual SAN</strong></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-1.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1314" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-1.png" alt="Install-VSAN-1" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span> để bắt đầu</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-2.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-2.png" alt="Install-VSAN-2" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Chấp nhận thỏa thuận sử dụng =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-3.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-3.png" alt="Install-VSAN-3" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-4.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1317" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-4.png" alt="Install-VSAN-4" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn đường dẫn cài đặt =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-5.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-5.png" alt="Install-VSAN-5" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn Full setup =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-6.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1319" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-6.png" alt="Install-VSAN-6" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-7.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1320" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-7.png" alt="Install-VSAN-7" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-8.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-8.png" alt="Install-VSAN-8" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn tùy chọn số 3 và <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-9.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1322" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-9.png" alt="Install-VSAN-9" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn đường dẫn đến file bản quyền mà bạn đã đăng ký</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-10.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-10.png" alt="Install-VSAN-10" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Review license và <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-11.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1324" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-11.png" alt="Install-VSAN-11" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Click <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Install</span> để tiến hành cài đặt</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-12.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1325" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-12.png" alt="Install-VSAN-12" width="504" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>Hoàn tất</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-13.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1326" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-13-620x330.png" alt="Install-VSAN-13" width="620" height="330" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-13-620x330.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-13-920x489.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-VSAN-13.png 1281w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Giao diện của chương trình</p>
<p><strong>2 &#8211; Cài đặt Starwind iSCSI Initiator</strong></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-1.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1327" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-1.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-1" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-2.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1328" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-2.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-2" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p>Đồng ý thỏa thuận sử dụng =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-3.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1329" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-3.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-3" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn đường dẫn cài đặt chương trình =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-4.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1330" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-4.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-4" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-5.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1331" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-5.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-5" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-6.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1332" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Install-iSCSI-Initiator-6.png" alt="Install-iSCSI-Initiator-6" width="504" height="393" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn Install để tiến hành cài đặt</p>
<p><strong>3 &#8211; Cấu hình Starwind Virtual SAN</strong></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-1.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1333" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-1-620x330.png" alt="Config-VSAN-1" width="620" height="330" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-1-620x330.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-1-920x489.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-1.png 1281w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Mở Starwind Management Console =&gt;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Add server</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-2.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1334" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-2.png" alt="Config-VSAN-2" width="430" height="477" /></a></p>
<p>Nhập địa chỉ IP của Starwind server, trong bài này sử dụng 127.0.0.1 (localhost) do cài chung máy</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-3.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1335" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-3-620x293.png" alt="Config-VSAN-3" width="620" height="293" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-3-620x293.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-3-920x435.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-3.png 1177w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn Connect</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-4.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1336" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-4.png" alt="Config-VSAN-4" width="367" height="146" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn đường dẫn lưu tập tin (ổ iSCSI)</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-5.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1337" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-5-620x293.png" alt="Config-VSAN-5" width="620" height="293" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-5-620x293.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-5-920x435.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-5.png 1177w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Add Target</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-6.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1338" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-6.png" alt="Config-VSAN-6" width="576" height="459" /></a></p>
<p>Paste IQN của máy cần kết nối iSCSI đến máy chủ. Mỗi phần mềm iSCSI Initiator mỗi máy đều có 1 IQN riêng</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-7.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1339" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-7.png" alt="Config-VSAN-7" width="576" height="459" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Create</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-8.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1340" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-8-620x324.png" alt="Config-VSAN-8" width="620" height="324" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-8-620x324.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-8-920x480.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-8.png 1065w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Add device</span> (ổ lưu trữ cho phép iSCSI Initiator kết nối)</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-9.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1341" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-9.png" alt="Config-VSAN-9" width="576" height="459" /></a></p>
<p>Đặt tên và dung lượng cho ổ</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-10.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1342" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-10.png" alt="Config-VSAN-10" width="576" height="459" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Create</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-11.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1343" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Config-VSAN-11.png" alt="Config-VSAN-11" width="576" height="459" /></a></p>
<p>Hoàn tất</p>
<p><strong>4 &#8211; Kết nối VSAN</strong></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-1.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1344" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-1-620x387.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-1" width="620" height="387" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-1-620x387.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-1.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Mở iSCSI Initiator chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Add Device</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-2.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1345" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-2.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-2" width="534" height="433" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Remote iSCSI device</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-3.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1346" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-3.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-3" width="534" height="433" /></a></p>
<p>Nhập địa chỉ IP của Starwind Virtual SAN Server và port (mặc định 3260)</p>
<p>Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-4.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1347" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-4-620x387.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-4" width="620" height="387" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-4-620x387.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-4.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn Target để kết nối</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-5.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1348" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-5.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-5" width="534" height="433" /></a></p>
<p>Kết nối thành công</p>
<p>Finish</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-6.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1349" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-6.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-6" width="348" height="187" /></a></p>
<p>Để sử dụng ổ đĩa, các bạn cần truy cập Disk Management của Windows</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-7.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1350" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-7.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-7" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Một cửa sổ hiện ra cho phép khởi tạo và cấu hình đĩa cứng (ổ iSCSI remote)</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-8.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1351" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-8.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-8" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-9.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1352" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-9.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-9" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Finish</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-10.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1353" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-10-620x213.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-10" width="620" height="213" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-10-620x213.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-10.png 625w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chuột phải vào ổ đĩa chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">New Volume</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-11.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1354" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-11.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-11" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-12.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1355" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-12.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-12" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn Simple =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-13.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1356" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-13.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-13" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Next</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-14.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1357" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-14.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-14" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Gán tên ổ đĩa cho ổ iSCSI</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-15.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1358" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-15.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-15" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn hệ thống tập tin là NTFS và tên ổ đĩa</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-16.png" rel="lightbox[1313]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1359" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Connect-VSAN-16.png" alt="Connect-VSAN-16" width="504" height="394" /></a></p>
<p>Hoàn tất, lúc này bạn có thể sử dụng ổ cứng như một ổ bình thường gắn trên máy ngoại trừ ổ bạn dùng được kết nối qua mạng</p>
